接口 LispList<T>

    public interface LispList<T>
    A lisp-like List.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法

      Get the first element of the list.

    • 方法详细资料

      • isEmpty

        boolean isEmpty()
        Return whether the list is empty or not.
        返回:
        true if this list is empty

      • car

        T car()
        Get the first element of the list. If the list is empty, a NoSuchElementException will be throwed.
        返回:
        the first element of the list

      • cdr

        LispList<T> cdr()
        Get the list without the first element. If the list is empty, a NoSuchElementException will be throwed.
        返回:
        the list without the first element
